item.description:
Sooo This month- is at Jeff's place! Yes again, he's given us a nice home to meet at- thank you Jeff!

The theme of the month? Don't you think we should have a Halloween theme? Scary - Dark- Crazy- Silly- Images! Share the best you got! Anyone been to Salem? Anyone been to a grave yard? Anyone have Halloween Parade photos? Trick or Treat?

Bring a treat or a photo to share!


See you there!
Donna and Scotty Pants
